          <h4 class="font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">Single-Wall (3–5mm) — General Crafts</h4>
          <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm mb-2">Best for lightweight projects: pet toys, art, decorative boxes, signage.</p>
          <p class="font-label text-xs text-secondary">Cost: RM 1.50–2.50 per sheet</p>
